title: Braided Hairstyles Fashion
description: Braided Hairstyles Fashion is a beauty game to be the coolest hairstylist! Meet our two main characters: Regina and Kiki and show your braiding skill. Brian, the hairstylist will tell you how it's done. Once you've got the perfect braid for the girls, customize it even more! Put on some accessories, clothes, change the hair color, whatever your heart desires!
